title: Wall St climbs as investors eye earnings
text:
Wall St climbs as investors eye earnings   01:22 
Stocks rose on Monday as investors turned their focus on corporate earnings and appeared less worried about the U.S.-led missile attacks in Syria. Fred Katayama reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
